    "The model-specific SHAP methods are designed to explain the specific models to decrease the calculation or loss of the complex models.",
    "They can only be used for a particular situation.",
    "In contrast, the kernel SHAP can be used for any model type.",
    "However, the SHAP method is a causal-inference-based methodology.",
    "The logic among AI models still needs to be clarified."
